All Classes

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Application
    Application class represents application that runs pizzeria simulation.
    Baker
    Baker class is abstract class that implements Runnable interface.
    Bakers
    Bakers class represents baker who generates orders and adds them to shared order queue.
    Configuration
    Configuration class represents configuration settings for pizzeria, including queue capacity, number of restaurants,cooking times for each restaurant, number of deliverers, and delivery capacities.
    Customer
    Customer class is abstract class that implements Runnable interface.
    Deliverer
    Deliverer class represents deliverer who picks up orders from shared order queue and delivers them to customers.
    MyQueue<T>
    MyQueue class is generic class represents thread-safe queue with capacity.
    Order
    Order class represents order with unique number and preparation time.
    Pizzeria
    Pizzeria class represents pizzeria with multiple restaurants, bakers, and deliverers that process orders through delivery system.
    Restaurant
    Restaurant class extends Baker class and represents restaurant processes orders through delivery system.
    Runner
    Runner class is responsible for starting Pizzeria application.
